title: Horror Movies - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/28/22
itunes:title: Horror Movies - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 10/28/22
description:
George Noory and author Kaedrich Olsen discuss popular horror movies like The Exorcist, The Conjuring and The Amityville Horror, what Hollywood gets right and wrong, and how misperceptions in popular movies may confuse people when they have paranormal experiences in real life.
